Description: Deepin Environment Awareness Daemon
 A system environment awareness module for deepin's built-in AI assistant.
 It runs as a background daemon, continuously sensing system changes and
 recording user operations, and exposes query interfaces and event signals
 via D-Bus for the AI assistant to better understand user context.
 .
 Key features:
  * Plugin-based sensors: window, file, clipboard, input, system, browser
  * SQLite storage with redaction and configurable retention
  * D-Bus interfaces: Context, History, System, Config, Events
  * Wayland/X11 dual-path support
  * Privacy-first: content redaction, no keystroke recording
